<ul>
  <li><strong>BUSCO</strong>: Sim&atilde;o et al. (2015). BUSCO: assessing genome assembly and
    annotation completeness with single-copy orthologs. <em>Bioinformatics</em> 31(19):3210-3212.</li>
  <li><strong>MAFFT</strong>: Katoh &amp; Standley (2013). MAFFT multiple sequence alignment
    software version 7. <em>Mol. Biol. Evol.</em> 30(4):772-780.</li>
  <li><strong>IQ-TREE 3</strong>: Wong et al. (2026). IQ-TREE 3: Phylogenomic inference software
    using complex evolutionary models.</li>
  <li><strong>wASTRAL</strong>: Zhang &amp; Mirarab (2022). Weighting by gene tree uncertainty
    improves accuracy of quartet-based species trees. <em>MBE</em> 39(12):msac215.</li>
  <li><strong>gCF/sCF</strong>: Minh et al. (2020). New methods to calculate concordance factors
    for phylogenomic datasets. <em>MBE</em> 37(9):2727-2733.</li>
</ul>
